OL,4,COlder workers 'see biggest jobs fall
OL,5,Csince 1980s'
OL,6, The pandemic has led to the biggest
OL,7, annual fall in employment for older
OL,8, workers since the 1980s, according to a
OL,9, new report.
OL,11,FThe decline in the employment rate for
OL,12,Fthe over-50s has been twice as big as
OL,13,Ffor those aged between 25 and 49.
OL,15,FThe Resolution Foundation also found
OL,16,Fthat after losing work, older workers
OL,17,Ftake the longest to return.
OL,19,FIt called on the government to tailor
OL,20,Fretraining opportunities to over-50s.
